{"tid":1439081,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【緊急】【勇武和理非全部同我入黎】","createTime":"2019-08-10T03:51:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T07:40:11.000Z","uid":294513,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a7ea41e54951ed0a2fb96cf46b25913143d33819","tid":1439081,"uid":294513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:51:42.000Z","msg":"眼見愈黎愈多分化Po真係忍唔住要屌<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化、不割蓆、不被捕</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>不分化</strong></span></span>係希望唔好比敵人分化勇武&amp;和理非既聯手，真正做到<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>兄弟爬山，各有各做！</strong></span></span>，將每個人既強項優點推哂出黎各有各做！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>不割蓆</strong></span></span>係希望和理非唔好因為前線行動升級而割蓆，甚至乎出賣前線（好似雨傘個時咁），唔撚係代表左膠都唔屌得！切記左膠都係要睇大圍風向，呢兩個月以黎每次左膠出現都會比人屌走確實令人欣慰（義士「拎」走梁耀忠個一幕請大家記清楚），但眼見而家左膠又開始做野⋯⋯記住！有左膠既存在就唔會有今日既成果（我指行動終於學識升級），如見左膠，即屌！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>不被捕</strong></span></span>係希望前線醒目啲，Be water 唔好同班狗硬碰硬，每一個手足被捕都係我地既損失，一個都不能少！有咩事第一時間走！打佢老母臭閪游擊戰，<span style=\"color: red;\">敵進我退 敵駐我擾 敵疲我打 敵退我追</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢幾日剩係計連登都好多分化po，係人係鬼真係未必個個都分到，但係唔該大家記住一點<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武唔好再鬧和理非，和理非都唔好再鬧勇武。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武係矛和理非係盾，想打贏呢場杖缺一不可！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好比機會泛民/左膠起大台，呢場運動咁成功就係因為冇大台</span></span><br />\n<br />\n或者過左呢兩個月大家都開始攰，但係其實我地連一個訴求都仲未爭取到既時候真係冇乜資格休息，當你攰既時候諗一諗<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">對唔對得住被捕既任何一個人</span></span>，香港人，加油，撐落去！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>光復香港，時代革命</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>沒有暴徒，只有暴政</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>勿信左膠，提防散水</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"b7246ddea0121786db16ce4899d0fc64edc19d1e","tid":1439081,"uid":294513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:52:40.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"bac46941aeb7c630be968c933f8ec35ec4db05bd","tid":1439081,"uid":294513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:52:51.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"d585942960d70270358390226dd6a300899bb00a","tid":1439081,"uid":294513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:53:02.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"4e0ad36c9ee797be816a2137f847db6d9a755ee1","tid":1439081,"uid":294513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:53:12.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"a769c1c7f9c2b1d098155eb945e7ee9997e1acf9","tid":1439081,"uid":294513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:53:23.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"e5514bee2b5dfe545d08ea87e168faa0b8069b14","tid":1439081,"uid":294513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:53:37.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"d3e87baa17c7a9e73903175e4e16277445c51582","tid":1439081,"uid":294513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:53:47.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"972e17b8d3466affc38b8fde78980d50112d60a3","tid":1439081,"uid":294513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:53:59.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"11eb2a8b6de865c1bfac8be7b0a6d3f9fedc735d","tid":1439081,"uid":294513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:54:09.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"367e8c30680a5742aa470ba0f650246782d5ff43","tid":1439081,"uid":294513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:54:22.000Z","msg":"10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" c